    "Id": "vehiclechassisdef_PILUM_ARROWIV",
    "Name": "Pilum (Arrow IV)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Pilum Heavy Tank (Arrow IV)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>4/6 (Wheeled)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>260 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Pilum Heavy Tank is a fast and maneuverable vehicle used by the Federated Commonwealth Armed Forces. It proved effective in combat against both the Clans and during the FedCom Civil War, particularly during the Eighth Crucis Lancers' last stand on Proserpina.\n\nIntroduced shortly after the original Pilum in 3059, this artillery variant replaces the LRM-15s with a single Arrow IV missile launcher. The vehicle carries 20 missiles across two ammunition bays, allowing for specialized ammunition.",
